reviewText: This is not even a remotely good deal at the current $116 price. You can get the four Alien films in the Alien Anthology for $25, the 3 Predator films in an "Own the moments" triple pack for $15. I don't know who would want to own the lousy AvP films, but if you do I'm sure they can be had for less than $10 each. So that's less than half of this bundle's price.
